{
  "stem": "15694.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there, soon-- I don't know how-- relations found us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, hours only in Katowice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just the station, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were offered by the Jewish community there, you-- yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mentioned it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only tea and sympathy, but also money, even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, in Krakow we were [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] dispersed, so to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mother and sister together with an uncle or other, an uncle of my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandfather's brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father to grandfather's sister and her husband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And myself in a nearby place which was the daughter of the family, also married.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, the people where my mother and sister went, the Kleinbergers, had two sons 10, 15 years older than myself already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- where my father went, they had two sons, sort of something in between, or rather nearer my age.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, the daughter had a little son of one year old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have to mention that because they will be part of the story later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And where we stayed, we were eating-- except at night-- we were eating all together with Mother and sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The place where Mother and sister stayed, if somebody know-- knows Krakow, it was the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And underneath, there was the coffee-- Cafe [POLISH] where-- quite an expensive cafe with cabaret.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And now, I went to a club which was frequented by youngsters my age, and mostly, of course, emigrees.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There, I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, it was the only teenage year I had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in my book, which I am going to mention later, I wrote about some practical hoaxes I played on my-- well, on the person who wooed the same girl as I did.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
